---
title: Chicken Korma Curry & Garlic Flatbreads with Veggies, Minty Yoghurt & Apricot Sauce
description: There's nothing like mildly-spiced curry made with coconut cream for a warming weeknight meal. Make sure to use the flatbreads and garlic rice to scoop up all that delicious goodness!
